rows.label: qst201614_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Miss!
Lovely to see you again!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0002
rows.name: It's you, from before...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0003
rows.name:
You know what?
I've been practicing a lot since then!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0004
rows.name:
I've totally learned to sing and play
the Torigonda at the same time!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0005
rows.name:
I've heard you've been singing
all around the world, too, Miss...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0006
rows.name:
So I thought I'd better apply myself,
and practiced a lot!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0007
rows.name: ...Oh my...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0008
rows.name: Hey, Miss...?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0009
rows.name: Would you mind listening to my song?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0010
rows.name: ...Not at all. Please, go ahead.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, that's really lovely...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0012
rows.name:
That means the world to me,
coming from the most awesome
person on Alst right now.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0013
rows.name: No, no... It wasn't flattery.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0014
rows.name:
You looked so joyful when you played,
that you filled me with joy too...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0015
rows.name:
I felt your joy as well, when you sang
in the streets of Torigo!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0016
rows.name: My song gave you...joy...?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0017
rows.name:
I've heard you're worried about
your singing, Miss. Is that true?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0018
qst201614_msg0019
rows.name:
Don't mind the people or the stage.
What you need to do, Miss, is put your
feelings into the song, then let it go.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0020
rows.name:
...Yes, you're right.
You're absolutely right.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0021
rows.name:
I don't need to get worked up about
the people who've come to listen...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0022
rows.name:
I just have to stay true to myself
and sing!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0023
rows.name:
Yes! Yes!
That's it, right there!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0024
rows.name:
Feeling better now,
Nanakoori?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0025
rows.name:
...Yes.
I think I'm going to sing now!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0026
rows.name: Tora looking forward!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0027
rows.name:
Teetapz also sure, if Nanakoori sing as
she always do, success is guaranteed.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0028
rows.name:
Yes...
I'll do my best!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0029
rows.name:
My song...
I hope the world's ready for it!
